data.description:
Here is your chance to own a lovely home in a beautiful subdivision. This home is close enough to schools, parks, shopping, entertaining and more and situated in a quite neighborhood to enjoy. 
3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, all appliances included. Home sits on a corner lot and has a spacious backyard with storage sheds and a large covered structure with power outlets and fans. Garage was converted to another large family room. 2 living spaces, dining space, kitchen with pantry, gas stove, microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator.
